ReadMe

Drill ID: JD_2026_06_W3_PetCareCenterApp

Class Name: PetCareCenterApp

Difficulty: Level 2 — Multi-Class Application

Estimated Time: 50–60 minutes

Actual Time Taken: 43 minutes

Written by: Chanwoo Park

Problem
Create a small pet care center management program using inheritance, interface, and ArrayList.

Requirements
- Create Pet as a parent class.
- Create Dog and Cat as child classes.
- Use CareService interface for care behavior.
- Store pets in an ArrayList.
- Search for pets and update their health score.

Learning Objective
Practice combining inheritance, interface implementation, polymorphism, ArrayList storage,
object search, method overriding, and state update logic.